2
00:02:49,485 --> 00:02:51,007
Are they
here yet?

3
00:02:51,086 --> 00:02:52,721
Hey, little sleepy head.

4
00:02:52,788 --> 00:02:54,188
Because I'm ready.

5
00:02:59,294 --> 00:03:02,080
You really are ready,
aren't you?

6
