(TRUCK HONKING)

7
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,351
Whoa, whoa!
Wait a second! Your coat!

8
00:03:19,114 --> 00:03:20,214
(EXCLAIMING)

9
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,157
We're all ready for you.

10
00:03:30,192 --> 00:03:32,077
Just need that balloon
payment to unload.

11
00:03:32,144 --> 00:03:35,579
We have it. It's just they
called Troy from Titus last night.

12
00:03:35,647 --> 00:03:37,649
The ski place?

13
00:03:37,717 --> 00:03:41,619
Do you have
the $4,372 or not?

14
00:03:41,687 --> 00:03:45,006
It was some emergency
with the lift.

15
00:03:45,073 --> 00:03:46,507
And he just took
off out of here

16
00:03:46,575 --> 00:03:49,193
without thinking,
with the money.

17
00:03:49,262 --> 00:03:50,395
Completely forgot
you were coming.

18
00:03:50,463 --> 00:03:51,696
So as soon
as he gets back...

19
00:03:51,763 --> 00:03:54,199
When's he getting back?

20
00:03:54,266 --> 00:03:56,784
When you come with the other half,
I'll have it.

21
00:03:56,936 --> 00:04:00,187
You don't get the other half
until I get the cash.

22
00:04:00,255 --> 00:04:02,574
This is the second time
you've dragged me out here.

23
00:04:02,641 --> 00:04:04,609
If you can't come up
with it by Christmas,

24
00:04:04,676 --> 00:04:07,044
