$1,500 deposit.

25
00:04:07,829 --> 00:04:10,198
Look, Mr. Versailles,

26
00:04:10,266 --> 00:04:12,750
I've got a good job
at Yankee One Dollar.

27
00:04:12,818 --> 00:04:15,520
They're probably going to make
me manager right after Christmas,

28
00:04:15,588 --> 00:04:18,289
