make the payments

29
00:04:18,357 --> 00:04:19,724
if you just leave
the house.

30
00:04:19,791 --> 00:04:23,295
Just call me when you have
the balloon payment.

31
00:04:26,132 --> 00:04:27,615
I'll call you.

32
00:04:36,158 --> 00:04:39,043
RICKY: Where are
they going?

33
00:04:39,111 --> 00:04:40,711
