53
00:05:29,577 --> 00:05:30,895
I don't know, Ricky.

54
00:05:30,962 --> 00:05:33,531
I can't believe you're not
even going to look for him.

55
00:05:33,599 --> 00:05:34,966
Where? Where do I look?

56
00:05:35,034 --> 00:05:36,534
The reservation!

57
00:05:36,602 --> 00:05:39,370
